data.description: This home has it all! Beautiful inside with plenty of space. Close to I-85 and all that Commerce has to offer! Wood floors throughout with a large open great room, kitchen and separate dining area. The Master is spacious and has a large bath with garden tub and separate shower. Two large bedrooms and a full bath, on the opposite side of the house, complete the main level. The finished lower level has two additional bedrooms and a full bath. The laundry is on this floor. Huge two car garage and a large yard for play and entertaining. So much space for the price! Now is the time to make your move!
